Class IEssDimension.EEssDimensionStorageCategory

java.lang.Object
  com.essbase.api.metadata.IEssDimension.EEssDimensionStorageCategory
All Implemented Interfaces:

Enclosing class:
IEssDimension
public static final class IEssDimension.EEssDimensionStorageCategory
extends java.lang.Object
implements IEssEnum

EEssDimensionStorageCategory class is the Dimension storage category. This is valid only for dimensions and attribute members. Optimizes the storage types of dimensions when the outline is configured for automatic optimization.

Version:
1.0, 04/04/2001
Author:
Srini Ranga
